snippet.title: Brutal Wolfenstein 3D V5.0 Episode 1 [100% EVERYTHING] 1440p 60fps
snippet.description:
Welcome to Brutal Wolfenstein Episode 1 ! 
In this video, I'll clear every level completely (100% kills, treasures and secrets) on  "Bring 'em on!" difficulty. All secrets will be found, all treasures will be looted and not a single NAZI will be spared. 

Levels:
Floor 1: 0:38
Floor 10(secret level): 6:24
Floor 2: 21:11
Floor 3: 34:03
Floor 4: 45:20
Floor 5: 56:07
Floor 6: 1:09:00
Floor 7: 1:18:04
Floor 8: 1:28:44
Floor 9: 1:39:18

Required files and Downloads:

GZDoom v4.1.0(Latest Version): 
https://zdoom.org/downloads

ZDL:
https://github.com/qbasicer/qzdl/releases/tag/v3.2.2.2-stable 

Brutal Wolfenstein v5.0:
https://www.moddb.com/mods/brutal-wolfenstein-3d/downloads/zmc-bwfinal

High Res pack:
https://www.moddb.com/mods/brutal-wolfenstein-3d/addons/brutal-wolfenstein-3d-high-resolution-pack

Flashlight:
https://www.moddb.com/mods/brutal-wolfenstein-3d/addons/brutal-wolfenstein-3d-flashlight

Mod load order in ZDL (launch with Doom2.wad):
ZMC-BWFinal.pk3
wolfTex.pk3
flashlight.pk3
